---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Mission | LibOS">
  <main class="container mission-page">
    <header class="mission-header">
      <div class="mission-badge">Our Vision</div>
      <h1 class="text-gradient">The Missing Manual for the Open Source World</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        LibOS is on a mission to turn the chaos of 200M+ GitHub repositories into actionable Engineering Playbooks.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="mission-content prose">
      <section>
        <h2>The Problem: The "Starred" Graveyard</h2>
        <p>
          GitHub is a graveyard of 10k+ star repositories that nobody knows how to actually integrate. Engineers spend more time "starring" than "building." Information is scattered, and the "synergy" between different open-source tools is never explained.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>The Solution: Engineering Playbooks</h2>
        <p>
          We don't just list repositories; we architect phased roadmaps that show you how to combine them into production-ready ecosystems. Whether you're a solo founder building an "Auto-Pilot Startup" or a developer mastering "Vibe Coding," LibOS gives you the blueprint.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <div class="card-icon">🚀</div>
          <h3>Phased Blueprints</h3>
          <p>Step-by-step guides for zero-to-production implementation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏗️</div>
          <h3>Ecosystem Mapping</h3>
          <p>See how tools like CrewAI, Midday, and Supabase work together.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-card">
          <div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
          <h3>Vibe Coding</h3>
          <p>A new philosophy for agentic software development and intent.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="mission-cta">
        <h2>Join the Revolution</h2>
        <p>
          The next wave of billion-dollar companies will be built by "teams of one" leveraging a fleet of open-source agents. We are here to provide the educational infrastructure that makes this possible.
        </p>
        <a href="/collections" class="btn-primary">Explore Playbooks</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .mission-page {
    padding-top: 8rem;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .mission-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .mission-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-neon);
    border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    border-radius: 99px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .mission-header h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .mission-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 4rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 6rem 0;
  }

  .mission-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-neon);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.02);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .mission-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .mission-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.03));
    border-radius: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
    background: var(--accent-neon);
    color: black;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .mission-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
